Manual iteration-13 curation ledger created from NCBI GDS searches for hypoxia/normoxia RNA-seq DEG candidates, GEO supplementary FTP listings, direct downloads of GSE225253 workbooks and family SOFT metadata, pandas workbook inspection, locked HIF-target orientation checks, and sha256sum of files under data/deg/raw/iter13. Active inclusion is limited to one GSE225253 source-family representative to avoid source-family inflation.
